Name: sheet

Synonyms: sheet, sheet dialog, sheet dialog box, sheet dialog boxes

Type: glossary

Description:
On <OS X|OS X systems>, a <dialog box> associated with a specific
window. A sheet appears within the window, sliding out from under the
<title bar>. The user can use other windows, but cannot use the sheet's
window until the sheet is dismissed.

References: title bar (glossary), OS X (glossary), dialog box (glossary)

Tags: windowing

